{
  "page": "Taking of Ashemark",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table style=\"margin: 4px 10%; border: 1px solid #aaa; background:#fbfbfb;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"padding: 2px 0 2px 0.5em;border-left: 10px solid #1e90ff;\">\n<div style=\"width: 50px;\"><img alt=\"Mbox notice.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/40px-Mbox_notice.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/60px-Mbox_notice.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/80px-Mbox_notice.png 2x\" />\n</div></td><td style=\"border: none; padding: 0.25em 0.9em; width: 100%;\"> <b>Note:</b> The title of this article is conjecture and may be subject to change.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background: #B0C4DE; text-align:center;\">Taking of Ashemark</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Conflict</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/War_of_the_Five_Kings\" title=\"War of the Five Kings\">War of the Five Kings</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Date</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/299_AC\" title=\"299 AC\">299&#160;AC</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Place</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Ashemark\" title=\"Ashemark\">Ashemark</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">Westerlands</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Result</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\">Stark</a> victory</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%; text-align:left;\">\n<tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Combatants</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Baratheon of King&#39;s Landing.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/6f/House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing.svg/33px-House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing.svg.png\" width=\"33\" height=\"36\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/6f/House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing.svg/50px-House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/6f/House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing.svg/66px-House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Throne\" title=\"Iron Throne\">Iron Throne</a></b>/ <a href=\"/index.php/House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing\" title=\"House Baratheon of King&#39;s Landing\">House Baratheon of King's Landing</a>:<br />\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Lannister.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Lannister.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/30px-House_Lannister.svg.png\" width=\"30\" height=\"33\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/45px-House_Lannister.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/60px-House_Lannister.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">Westerlands</a>, led by <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">House Lannister</a>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Marbrand\" title=\"House Marbrand\">House Marbrand</a></li></ul></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Stark.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Stark.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/30px-House_Stark.svg.png\" width=\"30\" height=\"33\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/45px-House_Stark.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/60px-House_Stark.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/index.php/King_in_the_North\" title=\"King in the North\">Kingdom of the North</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Trident\" title=\"King of the Trident\">the Trident</a></b>, led by <a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\">House Stark</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Robb_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Robb-2\">&#91;N 1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Commanders</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">Unknown</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      <a href=\"/index.php/File:Robb_Stark.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Robb Stark.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/5c/Robb_Stark.svg/20px-Robb_Stark.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/5c/Robb_Stark.svg/30px-Robb_Stark.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/5c/Robb_Stark.svg/40px-Robb_Stark.svg.png 2x\" /></a> King <a href=\"/index.php/Robb_Stark\" title=\"Robb Stark\">Robb Stark</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/File:Brynden_Tully.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Brynden Tully.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/9c/Brynden_Tully.svg/20px-Brynden_Tully.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/9c/Brynden_Tully.svg/30px-Brynden_Tully.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/9c/Brynden_Tully.svg/40px-Brynden_Tully.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Brynden_Tully\" title=\"Brynden Tully\">Brynden Tully</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Strength</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">Garrison of Ashemark</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      Less than 6,000 cavalry</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Casualties</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">Unknown</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      Unknown</td></tr>\n</tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>The <b>taking of Ashemark</b>  in the <a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">westerlands</a> is a <a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\">Stark</a> victory that follows the decisive victory at the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_Oxcross\" title=\"Battle of Oxcross\">Battle of Oxcross</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Prelude\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Prelude</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Battle\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Battle</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Aftermath\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Aftermath</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Notes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Prelude\">Prelude</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Taking_of_Ashemark&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Prelude\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Robb_Stark\" title=\"Robb Stark\">Robb Stark</a>, the new <a href=\"/index.php/King_in_the_North\" title=\"King in the North\">King in the North</a>, takes his army from the <a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">riverlands</a> into the <a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">westerlands</a> while Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Tywin_Lannister\" title=\"Tywin Lannister\">Tywin Lannister</a> is encamped at <a href=\"/index.php/Harrenhal\" title=\"Harrenhal\">Harrenhal</a>. Circumventing the border castles near the <a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Tooth\" title=\"Golden Tooth\">Golden Tooth</a>, Robb soundly defeats the new army being trained by Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Stafford_Lannister\" title=\"Stafford Lannister\">Stafford Lannister</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_Oxcross\" title=\"Battle of Oxcross\">Battle of Oxcross</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok32.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok32.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Battle\">Battle</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Taking_of_Ashemark&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Battle\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>In the aftermath of Oxcross, Robb takes several castles of the westermen, including the castle of <a href=\"/index.php/Ashemark\" title=\"Ashemark\">Ashemark</a>, the seat of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Marbrand\" title=\"House Marbrand\">House Marbrand</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok35.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok35.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> <a href=\"/index.php/Grey_Wind\" title=\"Grey Wind\">Grey Wind</a>, Robb's <a href=\"/index.php/Direwolf\" title=\"Direwolf\">direwolf</a>, slays a man during the taking of the castle.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> It is unknown if Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Damon_Marbrand\" title=\"Damon Marbrand\">Damon Marbrand</a> is taken captive.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Aftermath\">Aftermath</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Taking_of_Ashemark&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Aftermath\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Robb Stark continues plundering the westerlands,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> moving onto <a href=\"/index.php/Storming_of_the_Crag\" title=\"Storming of the Crag\">the Crag</a>. After learning that <a href=\"/index.php/Stannis_Baratheon\" title=\"Stannis Baratheon\">Stannis Baratheon</a> now <a href=\"/index.php/Siege_of_Storm%27s_End_(299)\" title=\"Siege of Storm&#39;s End (299)\">holds</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Storm%27s_End\" title=\"Storm&#39;s End\">Storm's End</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Catelyn_Stark\" title=\"Catelyn Stark\">Catelyn Stark</a> has Maester <a href=\"/index.php/Vyman\" title=\"Vyman\">Vyman</a> send a <a href=\"/index.php/Raven\" title=\"Raven\">raven</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/Riverrun\" title=\"Riverrun\">Riverrun</a> to Ashemark, hoping that a rider can then be sent to inform Robb of Stannis.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Notes\">Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Taking_of_Ashemark&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Robb-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Robb_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Houses <a href=\"/index.php/House_Flint_of_Widow%27s_Watch\" title=\"House Flint of Widow&#39;s Watch\">Flint of Widow's Watch</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Frey\" title=\"House Frey\">Frey</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Glover\" title=\"House Glover\">Glover</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Hornwood\" title=\"House Hornwood\">Hornwood</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Karstark\" title=\"House Karstark\">Karstark</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Manderly\" title=\"House Manderly\">Manderly</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Mollen\" title=\"House Mollen\">Mollen</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Mormont\" title=\"House Mormont\">Mormont</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/House_Umber\" title=\"House Umber\">Umber</a> are part of Robb's host during the <a href=\"/index.php/War_of_the_Five_Kings\" title=\"War of the Five Kings\">War of the Five Kings</a>. They may have accompanied him to Ashemark, but their participation in its capture has not been confirmed. <a href=\"/index.php/Barbrey_Dustin\" title=\"Barbrey Dustin\">Barbrey Dustin</a> says that <a href=\"/index.php/Cerwyn\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Cerwyn\">Cerwyns</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Slate\" title=\"House Slate\">Slates</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/House_Tallhart\" title=\"House Tallhart\">Tallharts</a> had men with Robb during the war as well.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Taking_of_Ashemark&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_46\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 46\">Chapter 46</a>, A Ghost in Winterfell.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok32.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok32.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_32\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 32\">Chapter 32</a>, Sansa III.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok35.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok35.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_35\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 35\">Chapter 35</a>, Bran V.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\">4.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-1\">4.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_14\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 14\">Chapter 14</a>, Catelyn II.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><